程序包 org.janusgraph.diskstorage.keycolumnvalue.keyvalue

接口 OrderedKeyValueStore

所有超级接口:
KeyValueStore
public interface OrderedKeyValueStore
extends KeyValueStore
A KeyValueStore where the keys are ordered such that keys can be retrieved in order.
作者:
Matthias Bröcheler (me@matthiasb.com);

  • 方法概要

    修饰符和类型 方法 说明
    RecordIterator<KeyValueEntry> getSlice​(KVQuery query, StoreTransaction txh)
    Returns a list of all Key-value pairs (KeyValueEntry where the keys satisfy the given KVQuery.
    Map<KVQuery,​RecordIterator<KeyValueEntry>> getSlices​(List<KVQuery> queries, StoreTransaction txh)
    Like getSlice(KVQuery, org.janusgraph.diskstorage.keycolumnvalue.StoreTransaction) but executes all of the given queries at once and returns a map of all the result sets of each query.

    • insert

      void insert​(StaticBuffer key, StaticBuffer value, StoreTransaction txh, Integer ttl) throws BackendException
      Inserts the given key-value pair into the store. If the key already exists, its value is overwritten by the given one.
      参数:
      key -
      value -
      txh -
      ttl -
      抛出:
      BackendException

    • getSlice

      RecordIterator<KeyValueEntry> getSlice​(KVQuery query, StoreTransaction txh) throws BackendException
      Returns a list of all Key-value pairs (KeyValueEntry where the keys satisfy the given KVQuery. That means, the key lies between the query's start and end buffers, satisfied the filter condition (if any) and the position of the result in the result list iterator is less than the given limit. The operation is executed inside the context of the given transaction.
      参数:
      query -
      txh -
      返回:
      抛出:
      BackendException

    • getSlices

      Map<KVQuery,​RecordIterator<KeyValueEntry>> getSlices​(List<KVQuery> queries, StoreTransaction txh) throws BackendException
      Like getSlice(KVQuery, org.janusgraph.diskstorage.keycolumnvalue.StoreTransaction) but executes all of the given queries at once and returns a map of all the result sets of each query. Only supported when the given store implementation supports multi-query, i.e. StoreFeatures.hasMultiQuery() return true. Otherwise this method may throw a UnsupportedOperationException.
      参数:
      queries -
      txh -
      返回:
      抛出:
      BackendException
